Package com.tapjoy

Interface Summary
TapjoyAwardPointsNotifier Any class calling TapjoyConnect.awardTapPoints(int, TapjoyAwardPointsNotifier) should implement TapjoyAwardPointsNotifier so it can receive the callback containing the virtual currency name/total info.
TapjoyEarnedPointsNotifier Notifier to inform the app whenever virtual currency has been earned.
TapjoyNotifier Any class calling TapjoyConnect.getTapPoints(TapjoyNotifier) should implement TapjoyNotifier so it can receive the callback containing the virtual currency name/total info.
TapjoySpendPointsNotifier Any class calling TapjoyConnect.spendTapPoints(int, TapjoySpendPointsNotifier) should implement TapjoySpendPointsNotifier so it can receive the callback containing the virtual currency name/total info.
TapjoyVideoNotifier  
TapjoyViewNotifier Callback methods which get triggered whenever a Tapjoy view opens or closes.
See TapjoyViewType for the different view types.
 

Class Summary
TapjoyConnect Created by Tapjoy.
Copyright 2010 Tapjoy.com All rights reserved.

For information about SDK integration, best practices and FAQs, please go to http://kc.tapjoy.com
TapjoyConnectFlag Flags used in TapjoyConnect.requestTapjoyConnect(android.content.Context, String, String, java.util.Hashtable) to define special startup options.

These flags can also be defined in the meta-data tags in AndroidManifest.xml.
TapjoyDisplayAdSize Supported banner ad sizes for Banner Ads.
TapjoyLog This class is used to control debug messages to the console for Tapjoy SDK related classes.
TapjoyVideoStatus Status codes used in the callbacks videos.
TapjoyViewType Different views created by the Tapjoy SDK.
